subject: GEOGRAPHY
text: On the accompanying map of part of the British Isles:

subject: GEOGRAPHY
text: Show the position of the counties of Somerset, Westmorland, Glamorgan and Kent.

subject: GEOGRAPHY
text: Mark and name the town at the mouth of each of the following rivers: Tweed, Wear, Nith.

subject: GEOGRAPHY
text: Insert the approximate position of the following and name each: Ben Nevis, Pennine Chain, Lake District, Grampian Mountains.

subject: GEOGRAPHY
text: Insert and name the following towns: Norwich, Carlisle, Plymouth, Inverness.
